\id GAL - Dawuro Full Bible Latin Version 
\h Galaatiyaa 
\toc1 P'awuloosi Galaatiyaa Asaw S'aafeedda Kiitaa 
\toc2 Galaatiyaa 
\toc3 Gal. 
\mt2 P'awuloosi 
\mt1 Galaatiyaa Asaw 
\mt2 S'aafeedda Kiitaa 
\imt1 Geluwaa 
\ip Yesuusi Ashshiyaawaa gidiyaawaa odiyaa mishiraachchuwaa k'aalay, dumma dumma sa'aan odettishshiinanne Ayihuda gidenna asaykka ammaniide akki akki biishshin, «Ammaniyaa asaa gidanaw Muse higgiyaa polanaw koshshiiyee koshshennee?» giyaa walassay ittippe denddeedda. He wode P'awuloosi, «Ammaniyaa asaa gidanaw Muse higgiyaa polanaw koshshenna; Yesuusan ooratsa de'uwaa demmanaw aan ammano asay, S'oossaa sintsan s'illanaw danddayiyaawe ammano s'alalaana» yaagiide tamaarissuwaa doommeedda. Shin K'eeri Iisiyaa giddon, «Asay S'oossaa sintsan s'illanaw Yesuusan ammaniyaawaa s'alalaa gidennaan, Muse higgiyaakka polanawunne k'as's'arettanaw koshshee» yaagiide P'awuloosa timirttiyaa p'alk'k'iyaa asatuu de'iino. 
\ip P'awuloosi hawaa Galatiyaa kiitaa s'aafeeddawe ha balaa timirttiyaan c'imetteedda asaa suure ammanoonne Ammanuwaa de'oo zaariide kaaletsanaassa. P'awuloosi koyro doommiidde, I barena, «Taani Yesuusi Kiitteeddawaa» yaagi erissiidde doommee. Yesuusi Kiitteeddawaa ootsiide Aa s'eeseeddawe S'oossaappe attin, asaa gidennawaanne k'ay I kiitetteeddawe Ayihuda gidenna asatuwaassa gidiyaawaa k'onc'c'issiide odee. Hewaannakka oyk'ettiide, Asay s'illanaw danddayiyaawe ammanuwaa s'alalaana gidiyaawaa odee. Wurssetsa shemppatuwaan Ammanuwaa eeshshay Yesuusa ammaniyaa ammanuwaappe kesiyaa siik'uwaappe pulttiyaawaa gidiyaawaa odee. 
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatoo Imetteedda K'antsa K'ofatuwaa 
\io1 Geluwaa \ior 1:1-10\ior* 
\io1 P'awuloosi S'oossaappe kiitetteedda maataa \ior 1:11—2:21\ior* 
\io1 S'oossaa aad'd'o keekatetsaa mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa \ior 3:1—4:31\ior* 
\io1 Kiristtinnaa la"atetsaanne ammanuwaa \ior 5:1—6:10\ior* 
\io1 Wurssetsaa k'utiyaa \ior 6:11-18\ior* 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Taani P'awuloosi, Yesuusi Kiristtoosinne k'ay hayk'uwaappe Aa dentseedda S'oossay Aawuu kiitteeddawaappe attin, asaappe woy asaa baggana kiitetteeddawaa gidikke.  
\v 2 Ha taaninne taananna de'iyaa ammaniyaa ishatuu ubbay, Galaatiyaa gadiyaan de'iyaa ammaniyaa asaa ubbaw sarotaa kiitteetto. 
\p  
\v 3 S'oossay nu Aawuunne nu Goday Yesuusi Kiristtoosi hinttenttoo aad'd'o keekatetsaanne sarotetsaa immo. 
\p  
\v 4 Nu S'oossaa, nu Aawuwaa sheniyaan Kiristtoosi ha iita oosuu oosettiyaa wodiyaappe nuuna ashshana mala, nu nagaraa diraw, bare huup'iyaa immeedda.  
\v 5 S'oossaw med'ippe med'inaa gakkanaw bonchchuu gido. Amen"i. 
\s1 Mishiraachchuwaa K'aalaa Tumuu Ittuwaa S'alalaa 
\p  
\v 6 Kiristtoosa aad'd'o keekatetsaan hinttentta s'eeseedda S'oossaa aggiide, hara wonggalaakko, hintte elleelliide, wooti simmeedditentto taw ooratsabaa gideedda.  
\v 7 Hinttentta bul"akkiyaawanttunne Kiristtoosa mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa geellayanaw koyyiyaa amareeda asatuu de'iinoppe attin, tumuppe hara mishiraachchuwaa k'aalay baawa.  
\v 8 Shin haray atto nuuna gidina, woy saluwaappe kiitanchchaa gidina, nuuni hinttenttoo kase odeedda mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaappe dummatiyaawaa hinttenttoo odiyaawaa gidooppe, I med'inaw shek'etteeddawaa gido.  
\v 9 Kase nuuni geeddawaadan, ha"ikka laa'entsuwaa taani oday; hintte akkeedda mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaappe dummatiyaawaa ooninne hinttenttoo odooppe, he uray med'inaw shek'etteeddawaa gido. 
\p  
\v 10 Hawe taana asaappe sabaa koyyiyaawaa malatissii? Malatissenna! Taani S'oossay lo"a giyaawaa koyyay. Woy taani asaa nashechchanaw koyyaytaa? Taani ha"ikka asaa nashechchanaw koyyiyaawaa gidooppe, Kiristtoosa ayile gidikke. 
\s1 P'awuloosi Yesuusi Kiitteeddawaa Gideedda Hanuwaa 
\p  
\v 11 Ta ishatoo, taani hinttenttoo odeedda mishiraachchuwaa k'aalay asaappe gidennawaa hinttenttoo oday.  
\v 12 Ayaw gooppe, taw Yesuusi Kiristtoosi k'onc'c'isseeddappe attin, taani mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa asaappe akkabeyikke; Asay taana tamaarissibeenna. 
\p  
\v 13 Kase taani Ayihuda ammanuwaan de'iyaa wode, waanaade de'aadditantto, hintte siseeddita; taani Kiristtoosa ammaniyaawantta k'aretay baynnaan yederssaaddinne d'ayissanaw baas'etaaddi.  
\v 14 Ta wode de'eedda asatuwaappe c'oratuwaa Ayihuda ammanuwaa higgiyaa naaguwaan aad'd'ay; nu aawotuwaa wogaa ooppenne aad'd'aade siik'aaddi. 
\p  
\v 15-16 Shin S'oossay bare aad'd'o keekatetsaan, taani biro ta daayi uluwaan de'ishshin, barew ootsanaw taana s'eeseedda; aabaa odiyaa mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa Ayihuda gidenna asaw taani odana mala, S'oossay bare Na'aa taw k'onc'c'issanaw koyyeedda wode, zorettanaw ookkonne babeykke.  
\v 17 Woy taappe kase Yesuusi kiitteeddawanttunna gakettanaw Yerusaalame babeykke; shin taani ellekka Arabiyaa geetettiyaa gadiyaa baad. Hewaappe Damask'k'o giyaa katamaa simmaaddi.  
\v 18 Heezzu laytsaappe guyyiyaan, P'es'iroosanna\f + \fr 1:18 \fq P'es'iroosa: \ft Giriike mas'aafay Keefaa yaagee. Biletsaykka Aramaayike k'aalaan «Zaallaa» giyaawaa.\f* gakettanaw Yerusaalame baade, aanana tammanne ichcheshu gallassaa uttaad.  
\v 19 Shin Yesuusi kiitteeddawanttuppe Godaa ishaa Yaak'oobappe attin, haratuwaanna gakettabeykki. 
\p  
\v 20 Taani hinttenttoo s'aafiyaawaan worii baawa; taani hinttenttoo wordduwaa odennawaa S'oossay markka! 
\p  
\v 21 Hewaappe guyyiyaan, Sooriyaa geetettiyaa gadiyaanne Kilk'k'iyaa geetettiyaa gadiyaa baad.  
\v 22 Yihudaan de'iyaa Kiristtoosan ammaniyaawanttu taananna eretaa gidikkino.  
\v 23 Shin hara asay, «Nuuna yederssi yuuyyiyaa bitanii hawaappe kase I d'ayissanaw koyyiyaa ammanuwaabaa ha"i odee» giyaawaa unttunttu  
\v 24 sisiide tabaan S'oossaa galateeddino. 
\c 2  
\s1 P'awuloosi Kiiteettowaa Gidiyaawe Haratuwaa Mataan Eretteedda 
\p  
\v 1 Hewaappe simmaade taani tammanne oyddu laytsaappe guyyiyaan, Barinabaasanna laa'entsuwaa Yerusaalame baadde, Tiitakka taananna akkaade baad.  
\v 2 S'oossay taw sas'aan k'onc'c'isseedda diraw baade taani ha"i ootsiyaa oosuu woy kase ootseeddawe mela attena mala, Kiristtoosan ammaniyaawantta kaaletsiyaawantta dumma shiishshaade, Ayihuda gidenna asaw taani odiyaa mishiraachchuwaa k'aalay ay malentto unttunttoo odaaddi.  
\v 3 Shin haray atto taananna de'iyaa Tiita I Giriike gadiyaa asaa gidishin, k'as's'aretto giide godetibeykkino.  
\v 4 Gidooppennekka, wordduwaan nuw ishatuwaa malati yiide, nuunanna walaketteedda c'ora asatuu Aa k'as's'aranaw koyyeeddino. He asatuu Kiristtoosa Yesuusan nuw de'iyaa nuuni koyyeeddawaadan hanana danddayiyaa la"atetsaa wochchiide d'iishanaw, wuu'ettiide nu giddo geliide nuuna ayile ootsanaw koyyeeddino.  
\v 5 Shin mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa tumatetsay hinttenttunna min de'ana mala, nuuni haray atto guutsa wodiyaakka unttunttoo moodettibeykko. 
\p  
\v 6 Shin kaappatuwaa malatiyaawanttu taw ayinne ooratsa k'ofaa immibeykkino; hawaa ayaw gaytaa gooppe, hawaappe kase unttunttu oona gidinakka taana metiyaabaa gidenna; S'oossay asaa som"iyaa s'eelliide pirddenna.\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Zar. 10:17\x* 
\v 7 Shin guyyeppe S'oossay P'es'iroosaw, Ayihudatoo mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa odiyaa hadaraa immeeddawaadan, tawukka Ayihuda gidenna asaw mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa odiyaa hadaraa immeeddawaa unttunttu be'eeddino.  
\v 8 Ayaw gooppe, P'es'iroosi Ayihudatoo Yesuusi kiitteeddawaa gideeddawaadan, taanikka S'oossaa wolk'k'aan Ayihuda gidenna asaw Yesuusi kiitteeddawaa gidaaddi.  
\v 9 K'ay kaaletsiyaawantta malatiide beettiyaawanttu, Yaak'oobi, P'es'iroossinne Yohaannisi, taw imetteedda aad'd'o keekatetsaa eriide, taananne Barnaabaasa nu kushiyaa oyk'k'iide saroteeddino. Taaninne Barnaabaasi Ayihuda gidenna asaa giddon ootsanaadan, k'ay unttunttu Ayihudatuwaa giddon ootsanaadan k'achchiide denddeeddo.  
\v 10 Unttunttu nuuna kaseppekka taani ootsanaw k'oppaadde de'iyaa hiyyeesatuwaa maaddanawaa s'alalaa k'ofisseeddino. 
\s1 P'awuloosi Ans's'ookiyaan P'es'iroosa  // Timirttiyaa P'alk'k'eedda 
\p  
\v 11 Shin P'es'iroosi Ans's'ookiyaa giyaa katamaa yeedda wode, I bayizzeedda diraw, k'onc'c'iyaan taani Aa, «Neeni bayizzanchchaa» yaagaad.  
\v 12 Ayaw gooppe, Yaak'ooba matappe kiitetteedda amareeda Asay yaanaappe kase Ayihuda gidenna asatuwaana k'umaa mee; shin unttunttu yeeddawaappe guyyiyaan, Ayihuda gidennawanttu ammaniyaawantta gidanaw k'as's'arettanaw koshshee giyaawanttoo yayyeedda diraw, miyaawaa essiide, Ayihuda gidennawanttuppe shaaketteedda.  
\v 13 K'ay yekko ammaneedda Ayihudatuu P'es'iroosanna yashshaa doommeeddino; haray atto Barnnaabaasikka unttunttunna yashshanchcha gideedda. 
\p  
\v 14 Shin unttunttu mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa tumatetsaadan, suure hamettennawaa be'aade, P'es'iroosa he ubbaa asaa sintsan, «Neeni S'oossaa asaa Ayihuda gidaadde, unttunttuudan gidennaan S'oossaa asaa gidenna Ayihuda gidennawanttudan de'aa; shin yaatina, wootaade Ayihuda gidennawantta, ‹Ayihudatuwaadan de'ite› gaade gidday?» yaagaad. 
\s1 Ayihudatuukka Ayihuda Gidennawanttukka  // Attiyaawe Ammanuwaana 
\p  
\v 15 Nuuni yeletaan Ayihuda; «Nagaranchcha gideedda Ayihuda gidenna asatuwaa» gidokko.  
\v 16 Hewaa gidooppekka, Asay Yesuusi Kiristtoosa ammaniide S'oossaa sintsan s'illanaappe attin, Muse higgiyaa naaguwaan s'illennawaa ereeddo; ashuwaa mayyeedda Asay ubbay Muse higgiyaa naaguwaan s'illenna diraw, nuuni nu huup'ewukka Muse higgiyaa naaguwaan gidennaan, Kiristtoosan ammaniide s'illana mala, Kiristtoosi Yesuusan ammaneeddo.\x - \xo 2:16 \xt Maz. 143:2; Rom. 3:20, 22\x* 
\p  
\v 17 Shin nuw Kiristtoosan de'iyaa ittippetetsaan s'illanaw koyyiyaawantta gidiide, nu huup'ew nagaranchcha gidiide beettooppe, yaatina Kiristtoosi nagaraa tamaarissiyaawe? Hewe mulekka worddo!  
\v 18 Ayaw gooppe, itti kaallakka agga diggeeddawaa taani laa'entsuwaa ootsiyaawaa gidooppe, taani ta huup'ew higgiyaa mentsiyaawaa gidiyaawaa erissay.  
\v 19 Taani Kiristtoosaw pas'a de'ana mala, higgiyaa baggana higgew hayk'k'aaddi.  
\v 20 Taani Kiristtoosanna Aa mask'k'aliyaa bolla misimaariyan d'ishettaade kak'k'etaad; simmi, ha"i pas'a de'iyaawe taana gidikke. Shin Kiristtoosi ta giddon de'ee; taani ha"i de'iyaa de'uu, taana siik'iide, ta diraw, bare huup'iyaa immeedda S'oossaa Na'aan de'iyaa ammanuwaana.  
\v 21 Taani S'oossaa aad'd'o keekatetsaa is's'ikke; Asay higgiyaa baggana s'illotetsaa demmiyaawaa gidooppe, Kiristtoosi c'oo mela hayk'k'eedda guussaa. 
\c 3  
\s1 S'illotetsay Ammano S'alalaan Beettee 
\p  
\v 1 Akeekay baynna Galaatiyaa asatoo, taani hinttena Kiristtoosi mask'k'aliyaa bollan misimaariyan d'ishettiide kak'etteeddawaa k'onc'c'issaade tamaarissaad. Yaatina, tumoo hintte eeno geena mala, hinttentta biteeddawe oonee?  
\v 2 Ane taw ha itti yewuwaa s'alalaa odite: S'oossaa Ayaanaa, higgii giyaawaa naagiide akkeedditee woy ammanuwaan sisiide akkeedditee?  
\v 3 Hinttenttu hewaa keena eeyee? S'oossaa Ayyaanan de'uwaa doommiide, ha"i hintte wolk'k'aan poliitee?  
\v 4 Hinttenttu daaburaa ubbaw ayinne maaduu baawee? Tuma maaduu de'ee.  
\v 5 Yaatina, S'oossay hinttenttoo Geeshsha Ayaanaa immiyaawenne hintte giddon malaataa ootsiyaawe, Muse higgiyaa hintte ootseedda diraassee? Woy mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa sisiide, hintte ammaneedda diraassee? 
\p  
\v 6 Hawaadankka, Abraahaamo S'oossaa ammaneedda diraw, S'oossay Aa s'illuwaadan s'eelleedda.  
\v 7 Hewaa diraw, ammaniyaawanttu Abraahaame zare\f + \fr 3:7 \fk Ammaniyaawanttu Abraahaame zare: \ft S'oossay Abraahaama dooreedda; he diraw ooninnekka Abraahaame na'aa geetetteeddawe, S'oossaa na'aa gidiyaawe ammanetteeda. \xt 3:29\ft  s'eellite.\f* gidiyaawaa erite.\x - \xo 3:7 \xt Rom. 4:16\x* 
\v 8 S'oossay Ayihuda gidenna asaa ammanuwaan s'illissanawaa S'oossaa Mas'aafay kaseti be'iide, «Ha alamiyaan de'iyaa Asay ubbay neenan anjjettana» yaagiide, mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa Abraahaamoo kasetiide odeedda.\x - \xo 3:8 \xt Dom. 12:3\x* 
\v 9 Hewaa diraw, Abraahaamo ammaniide anjjetteeddawaadan, ammaniyaawanttu aawaadakka anjjettana. 
\p  
\v 10 Higgiyaa oosuwaan ammanettiide de'iyaawanttu ubbay shek'aa giddon de'iino; ayaw gooppe, S'oossaa Mas'aafay, «Higgiyaa mas'aafan s'aafetteedda ubbabaan de'ennawenne polennawe ooninne shek'etteeddawaa» yaagee.  
\v 11 S'oossaa Mas'aafay, «S'oossaa sintsaan s'illatuu aan ammanettiide de'uwaan de'ana»\f + \fr 3:11 \fq «S'oossaa sintsaan s'illatuu aan ammanettiide de'uwaan de'ana»: \ft S'oossay akkeedda Asay ammanuwaappe denddeeddawaan de'uwaan de'ee.\f* giyaa diraw, ooninne S'oossaa sintsan higgiyaa naagiyaawaan s'illennawe eretteeddawaa.  
\v 12 Higgii ammanuwaan baasetti ek'k'ibeenna; shin S'oossaa Mas'aafay, «Higgii giyaawaa poliyaawe aan de'uwaan de'ana» yaagee.\x - \xo 3:12 \xt Wog. 18:5\x* 
\p  
\v 13 S'oossaa Mas'aafan, «Mitsaa bolla kak'etti hayk'k'iyaa ooninne shek'etteeddawaa» geetetti s'aafetteedda diraw, Kiristtoosi nu diraw shek'etteeddawaa gidiide, nuuna higgiyaa shek'aappe wozi akkeedda.\x - \xo 3:13 \xt Zar. 21:23\x* 
\v 14 Kiristtoosi hewaa ayaw ootseedee gooppe, S'oossay immana gooppe, Geeshsha Ayaanaa nuuni ammanuwaan akkanaaddaaninne Abraahaame anjjuu bare baggana Ayihuda gidenna asaa gakkana mala giide ootseedda. 
\s1 Higgii Hidootaa K'aalaa Kolenna 
\p  
\v 15 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani Asay giyaawaadan hinttenttoo gay; haray atto laa"u asatuu itti yewuwaa haasayiide, c'aak'uwaa wotseeddawaappe hini baggan, ooninne he c'aak'uwaa billanaw woy harabaa he c'aak'uwaa bolla gujjanaw danddayenna.  
\v 16 Abraahaamonne Aa zarii S'oossay sintsappe immana giide haasayeeddawaa siseeddino. S'oossaa Mas'aafay c'ora asaw haasayiyaawaadan, «Ne zeretsatoo» geena; waagii gooppe, «Ne zarew» yaagee. Hewenne, itti asaa s'alalaa gee; ikka Kiristtoosa.\x - \xo 3:16 \xt Dom. 12:7\x* 
\p  
\v 17 Taani giyaawe hawaa; S'oossay Abraahaamoo c'aak'k'iidde, ha c'aak'uwaa taani naagana yaageedda. Oyddu s'eetanne hattamu laytsaappe guyyiyaan yeedda Muse higgii S'oossay wotseedda ha c'aak'uwaa d'ayissanawunne sintsappe immana giide haasayeeddawaa digganaw danddayenna.\x - \xo 3:17 \xt Kes. 12:40\x* 
\v 18 Ayaw gooppe, S'oossay immiyaa laatay higgiyan beettiyaawaa gidooppe, yaatina S'oossay sintsappe immana giide, k'aalaa geleeddawaana gidenna giyaawaa; shin S'oossay immana giide k'aalaa geleeddawaan laataa Abraahaamoo immeedda. 
\p  
\v 19 Yaatina, higgii ayaw de'ii? Higgii bayizzo oosuwaa gidiyaabay ayentto bessanaw S'oossay immana giide haasayeedda Abraahaame zarii yaana gakkanaw gujetteedda; kiitanchchaa baggana Muse gaannatiyaawaan imetteedda.  
\v 20 Gaannay itti uraa s'alalaassa gidenna; shin S'oossay ittuwaa. 
\s1 Higgiyaa K'ofaa 
\p  
\v 21 Yaatina, S'oossay sintsappe immana giide haasayeeddawaa, itti higgii, «Hanenna» yaagii? A"a! Hewaa geena. Ayaw gooppe, higgii asaw de'uwaa immanaw danddayiyaabaa gidooppe, s'illotetsaykka tumu higgiyaa azazettiyaawaappe beettee giyaawaa.  
\v 22 Shin Yesuusi Kiristtoosa ammanina, S'oossay sintsappe immana giide k'aalaa geleedda la"atetsay, ammaniyaawanttoo imettana mala, Asay ubbay nagaraw moodettiide de'iyaawaa, S'oossaa Mas'aafay odee. 
\p  
\v 23 Shin kase ha ammanuu yaanaw, sintsappe k'onc'c'ana ammanoo higgii nuuna k'ashetteedda asaadan gorddi wotseedda.  
\v 24 Hewaa diraw, nuuni ammanuwaan s'illana mala, Kiristtoosi yaana gakkanaw higgii nuuna naagiyaawaa gideedda.  
\v 25 Shin ha"i simmi ammanuu yeedda diraw, higgii hawaappe sintsaw nuuna naagiyaawaa gidenna. 
\p  
\v 26 Hinttenttu ubbay ammanuwaa baggana Kiristtoosa Yesuusan ittuwaa gideedda S'oossaa naanaa.  
\v 27 Ayaw gooppe, hintte Kiristtoosanna ittuwaa gidana mala s'ammak'etteedda ubbatuu Kiristtoosa mayyeeddita.  
\v 28 Hewaa diraw, Ayihuda asaa giddoninne Giriike asaa giddon dummatetsay baawa; ayiliyaa woy womaannuwaa giddon dummatetsay baawa; attumawaa woy mac'c'a asaa giddon dummatetsay baawa. Ayaw gooppe, hinttenttu ubbaykka Kiristtoosa Yesuusan itti asaa.  
\v 29 Hinttenttu Kiristtoosawaa gidooppe, simmi hinttenttu Abraahaame zare;\f + \fr 3:29 \fq Abraahaame zare: \ft Ha"i nuuni Abraahaame golle asaa. Hewaassa P'awuloosi Galaatiyaa asaw odiidde, itti Asay Yesuusa ammaneedda ammanuwaan Abraahaamew tumu na'aa yaagettiide s'eegettee. Hewaa guussay S'oossaa na'aa guussaa. \xt 3:7\ft  s'eellite.\f* k'ay S'oossay sintsappe immana giide k'aalaa geleeddawaa laattiyaawantta. 
\c 4  
\s1 Nuuni S'oossaa Naanaa Gidiyaawaa 
\p  
\v 1 Shin akeekite; bare aabbuwaa laattiyaa na'ay na'atetsaan de'iidde, de'iyaawaa ubbaw godaa gidooppekka, ayilatuwaappe aw dummatiyaasay baawa.  
\v 2 Shin bare aabbu geedda wodii wurana gakkanaw, Aa hadaraa akkeeddawanttu kushiyaaninne Aa miishshaa naagiyaawanttu kushiyan de'ee.  
\v 3 Hawaadan nuunikka k'ay na'atetsaan de'iyaa wode, ha alamiyaa mooddiyaa ayyaanatoo ayileteeddo.  
\v 4 Shin yaanaw bessiyaa wodii gakkeedda wode, S'oossay mac'c'awunippe yelettowaa, Muse higgew moodettiyaa asaa garssan yeletteeddawaa, bare Na'aa kiitteedda.  
\v 5 Ayaw kiitteeddee gooppe, higgiyan moodettiide de'iyaawantta wozanawunne nuuna bare naanaa ootsanaw kiitteedda. 
\p  
\v 6 S'oossay hintte Aa naanaa gidiyaa diraw, «Abbabboo, ta Aabboo» giide waassiyaa bare Na'aa Ayaanaa, nu wozanaa giddo kiitteedda.  
\v 7 Hewaa diraw, hawaappe sintsaw neeni S'oossaa na'aa gidiyaawaappe attin, ayile gidakka; k'ay neeni Aa na'aa gidooppe, Kiristtoosa baggana S'oossay k'aalaa geleeddabaa laattiyaawaa. 
\s1 P'awuloosi Galaatiyaa Asaabaa Hirggeedda 
\p  
\v 8 Shin hintte hawaappe kase S'oossaa erennaan de'iidde, tuma gidenna s'oossatoo ayile gidiide eeno geeddita.  
\v 9 Shin ha"i S'oossaa eriide, ubbaakka S'oossaan erettiide, laafanne k'ay kad'etteedda ha ayyaanatuwaakko waaniide simmiitee? Shiretti simmi, ayile gidiide, laa'entsuwaa unttunttoo eeno gaanaw koyyiitee?  
\v 10 Dummateedda gallassattuwaa, agenatuwaa, wodetuwaanne laytsatuwaa hintte loytsi naaguwaan ayileteeddita.  
\v 11 Taana hinttebay yashshee; taani hinttenttoo c'oo gaade mela daaburaadditaashsha? 
\p  
\v 12 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani hinttenttuudan haneedda diraw, «Hinttenttukka taanaadan hanite» gaade, hinttentta woossay; hintte taana ayinne naak'k'ibeykkita.  
\v 13 Taani koyro hinttenttoo mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa odeeddawe taana harggissishshiina gidiyaawaa hintte eriita.  
\v 14 Taw pas'atetsay d'ayiide, hinttenttoo paac'e gidinakka, taana kad'ibeykkita; shenetikkabeykkita. Hewaa diraa ubbaa taana S'oossaa kiitanchchaa mokkiyaawaadan, woy Kiristtoosa Yesuusa mokkiyaawaadan mokkeeddita. 
\p  
\v 15 Yaatina, hekko hintte nashettiyaawe beettena! Taana gidooppe, hinttenttoo danddayettiyaabaa gidina, taw hintte hinttenttu ayfiyaa wooc'i imminttonne is's'ennawaa markkattay.  
\v 16 Yaatina taani hinttenttoo tumuwaa odiyaa diraw, hintte morkke gidaytaa? 
\p  
\v 17 Hara asatuu hinttenttoo k'arettiyaawaa malatiino; shin unttunttu k'ofay lo"enna; ayaw gooppe, hintte unttunttoo k'arettana mala, taappe hinttentta shaakkanaw koyyiino.  
\v 18 Shin taani hintte matan de'iyaa wode s'alalaan gidennaan, ubbaa wodekka lo"obaan hintte koyettiyaawantta gidooppe lo"a. 
\p  
\v 19 Ta siik'o naatoo, Kiristtoosa med'etay hinttenttun beettana gakkanaw, mac'c'awuno oytsay sakkiyaa keenaa, taani hintte diraw sakettay.  
\v 20 Shin taani hinttenttoo hirggiyaa diraw, ha"i hintte mata baade hinttenttunna doonaan haasayantto, darii dosay. 
\s1 Aggaarinne Saari Leemisuwaa 
\p  
\v 21 Muse higgiyan moodettiide de'anaw koyyiyaawanttoo, higgii giyaawaa sisikkitee? Ane taw odite.  
\v 22 Ayaw gooppe, S'oossaa Mas'aafay, «Abraahaamoo danggaas'irattippenne godattippe yeletteedda laa"u naanay de'iino» yaagee.\x - \xo 4:22 \xt Dom. 16:15; 21:2\x* 
\v 23 Shin danggaas'iratti na'ay Asay na'aa yeliyaa maaraadankka yeletteedda; k'ay godatti na'ay, S'oossay sintsappe immana giide k'aalaa geleeddawaan yeletteedda. 
\p  
\v 24 Ha laa"u mac'c'awanttu laa"u c'aak'k'oo gidiyaa leemiso. Unttunttuppe ittinna, Musew higgii imetteedda Siinaa Deriyaappe c'aak'uu yeeddawunna, bare naanaa ayiletetsaw yelaaddu; izakka Aggaaro.  
\v 25 Ha Aggaara Arabiyaa geetettiyaa gadiyaan de'iyaa Siinaa Deriyaan leemisettaw; k'aykka ha"i de'iyaa Yerusaalamen leemisettaw; ayaw gooppe, Yerusaalame katamay bare giddon de'iyaa asaa ubbaanna Muse higgiyaa ayiletetsaan de'ee.  
\v 26 Shin saluwaan de'iyaa Yerusaalame ayiletetsaan de'ukku; iza nuw aatto gideedda Saaro.  
\v 27 Ayaw gooppe, S'oossaa Mas'aafay, 
\q1 «Hannee, yelabeenna mantsattee, nashetta; 
\q2 yeluwaa oytsay oyk'k'i erennawunnee, 
\q2 ne kooshshaa d'ok'k'u ootsaade ilila! 
\q2 Ayaw gooppe, bare asinaana 
\q2 de'iyaa mac'c'awunippe, 
\q2 barekka de'iyaa mac'c'awuniw 
\q2 c'ora naanay de'ana» 
\m yaagee.\x - \xo 4:27 \xt Isa. 54:1\x* 
\p  
\v 28 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, nuunikka Saari na'aa Yisaak'aadan, S'oossay sintsappe immana giide k'aalaa geleedda naanaa.  
\v 29 Shin he wode asaa maaraadan yeletteeddawe, S'oossaa Ayyaanay geeddawaadan yeletteeddawaa yederssi diggowaadan, ha"ikka hewaa mala.\x - \xo 4:29 \xt Dom. 21:9\x* 
\v 30 Shin S'oossaa Mas'aafay waagii? «Danggaas'iratti na'ay godatti na'aanna ittippe laattenna diraw, danggaas'iratto izi na'aanna ittippe kessa yedda» yaagee.\x - \xo 4:30 \xt Dom. 21:10\x* 
\v 31 Hewaa diraw, taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, nuuni godatti naanaa gidiyaawaappe attin, danggaas'iratti naanaa gidokko. 
\c 5  
\s1 Kiristtoosan Ayiletetsaappe Kesussaa 
\p  
\v 1 Nuuni ayiletetsay baynnaan, de'ana mala, Kiristtoosi nuuna ayiletetsaappe kesseedda; simmi minniide ek'k'ite; laa'entsuwaa ayiletetsaa morgge mitsaan waas'ettoppite. 
\p  
\v 2 Sisite, taani P'awuloosi, hinttentta yaagay; hintte k'as's'arettiyaawaa gidooppe, Kiristtoosi hinttentta ayinne maaddenna.  
\v 3 K'as's'arettiyaa ubbatuu higgii giyaawaa ubbaa poliide naaganaw bessiyaawaa gujjaade k'ofetsay.  
\v 4 Higgiyaa naagiide s'illanaw koyyiyaawanttoo, Kiristtoosappe shaaketteeddita; S'oossaa aad'd'o keekatetsaappekka kunddeeddita.  
\v 5 Nuuna gidooppe, nuuni S'oossaa Ayaanaa baggana ammanuwaan s'illanaw nashechchaan naageetto.  
\v 6 Ayaw gooppe, nuuni Kiristtoosi Yesuusanna ittippe de'ooppe, siik'uwaan ootsiyaa ammanuwaappe attin, k'as's'arettinakka, k'as's'arettennaan agginakka nuuna ayinne maaddenna. 
\p  
\v 7 Kase lo"o wos's'iita; shin tumatetsaw hintte eeno geena mala, oonee hinttentta diggeeddawe?  
\v 8 Ha c'imuu hinttentta s'eeseedda S'oossaappe yibeenna.  
\v 9 Asay giyaawaadan, guutsa irshshuu munak'aa ubbaa dentsee.  
\v 10 Hinttenttu harabaa k'oppennawaa taani S'oossaan ammanettay; shin hinttentta metiyaa uray oona gidooppenne, S'oossaappe bare pirddaa akkanawaa. 
\p  
\v 11 Shin taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani hawaa gakkanaw k'as's'aray koshshiyaawaa odiyaawaa gidooppe, taana ayaw yederssiinoo? Hewe tuma gidooppe, taani Kiristtoosa mask'k'aliyaabaa tamaarissina ayinne metiyaabay baawa.  
\v 12 Hinttentta metootsiyaawanttu barentta barenttookka goyreerikkinooshsha! 
\p  
\v 13 Hinttentta gidooppe, taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, ayiletetsaappe kesanaw s'eesetteeddita. Gidooppennekka ayiletetsaappe hintte keseeddawaan, hintte asatetsaa amuu hinttentta mooddoppo. Hewaa diraa siik'uwaan ittuu ittoo moodettite.  
\v 14 Ayaw gooppe, higgii ubbay itti haasayan k'ashetteedda; ikka, «Ne shooruwaa ne huup'iyaadan siik'a» yaagiyaawaa.\x - \xo 5:14 \xt Wog. 19:18\x* 
\v 15 Shin hintte ittuu ittuwaanna sa'ettiyaawaanne meetettiyaawaa gidooppe, hintte hintte giddon wurenna mala naagettite. 
\s1 Ayyaanaanne Ashuwaa 
\p  
\v 16 Shin sisite; S'oossaa Ayyaanay hinttentta kaaletsiyaawaa gidooppe, hintte ashuwaa amuwaa mulekka polikkita.  
\v 17 Ayaw gooppe, nu ashuu amottiyaawaa Geeshsha Ayyaanay is's'ee; k'ay Geeshsha Ayyaanay amottiyaawaa nu ashuu is's'ee; hawanttu ittuu ittuwaanna is'ettiino. Hewaa diraw, hintte dosiyaawaa ootsanaw danddaykkita.  
\v 18 Shin S'oossaa Ayyaanay hinttentta kaaletsiyaawaa gidooppe, Muse higgii hinttentta mooddenna. 
\p  
\v 19 Ashuwaa oosuu eretteeddawaa; ikka ayee gooppe, woshummiyaawaa, tunatetsaa, aad'd'eedda tunatetsaa oosuwaa,  
\v 20 eek'aw goyinniyaawaa, bitiyaawaa, morkketetsaa, palumaa, k'anaatiyaawaa, hank'k'uwaa, barena dosiyaawaa, walak'ettiyaawaa, ittuu ittuwaappe shaakettiyaawaa,  
\v 21 asaawaa amottiyaawaa, matsottiyaawaa, yetsanchchaa gidiyaawaanne hawantta malatiyaawantta. Kasekka taani hinttenttoo odeeddawaadan, hawantta malatiyaawantta ootsiyaawanttoo S'oossaa kawutetsaan geliyaasay baawa. 
\p  
\v 22 Shin Geeshsha Ayaanaa ayfii, siik'uwaa, nashechchaa, sarotetsaa, danddayaa, keekatetsaa, lo"otetsaa, ammanettiyaawaa,  
\v 23 ashikketetsaa, bare huup'iyaa naagiyaawaa. Hewantta malatiyaawantta diggiyaa higgii baawa. 
\p  
\v 24 Kiristtoosa Yesuusabaa gidiyaawanttu barenttu asatetsaa Aa iita k'ofaannanne Aa amuwaanna ittippe mask'k'aliyaa bollan misimaariyan d'ishiide kak'k'eeddino.  
\v 25 Nuw Geeshsha Ayyaanay de'uwaa immowaappe guyyiyaan, nuuna k'ay I kaaletso.  
\v 26 Ane otorettiyaawaa, woy ittuu ittuwaa hank'k'etsiyaawaa, woy ittuu ittuwaa k'anaatiyaawaa aggoytte. 
\c 6  
\s1 Ittuu Ittuwaanna Maadettiyaawaa 
\p  
\v 1 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, hinttenan Geeshsha Ayyaanan de'iyaawanttu itti uray ay bayizzuwaa ootsiide, beettooppekka, ashikketetsaa ayyaanan Aa suurissite; k'ay hintte paac'ettenna mala, hintte huup'iyaa naagite.  
\v 2 Ittuu ittuwaa tookuwaa tookkite; hewaa ootsiyaawaan Kiristtoosa higgew azazettiita.  
\v 3 Ayaw gooppe, itti uray ayinne hanennaan de'iidde, ittibaa I haneeddawaa aw malatooppe, bare huup'iyaa c'immee.  
\v 4 Shin Asay ubbay huup'iyaan huup'iyaan bare oosuwaa paac'c'o; hewaappe guyyiyaan, hara asaawaana likkennaan, bare huup'e oosuwaa s'alalaan ammanettiyaawaa demmana.  
\v 5 Ayaw gooppe, Asay ubbay huup'iyaan huup'iyaan bareppe naagettiyaawaa ootsana bessee. 
\p  
\v 6 Shin S'oossaa k'aalaa tamaariyaawe barew de'iyaa lo"obaa ubbaa barena tamaarissiyaawaanna shaakko. 
\p  
\v 7 Hinttentta hintterekka c'immoppite. Ooninne S'oossaa bolla k'iliic'anaw danddayenna; ayaw gooppe, Asay bare zeriyaawaa zaaretsiide k'oyc'ana.  
\v 8 Bare ashuwaa amuwaan zeriyaawaa gidooppe, ashuwaa amuwaappe hayk'uwaa k'oyc'ana. Shin S'oossaa Ayyaanan zeriyaawaa gidooppe, S'oossaa Ayyaanaappe med'inaa de'uwaa k'oyc'ana.  
\v 9 Ane lo"o oosuwaa ootsanaw minnoytte. Ayaw gooppe, nuuni min ootsooppe, k'oyc'iyaa wodii sintsappe yaanawaa.  
\v 10 Hewaa gidooppe ha ootsanaw nuuni danddayiyaawaan, asaa ubbaw lo"obaa ootsoytte; shin ubbaappe aatsiide, nuunanna ammanuwaan de'iyaawanttoo lo"obaa ootsoytte. 
\s1 Wurssetsaa Zoriyaanne Sarotaa 
\p  
\v 11 Taani ta kushiyan, ay mala wolk'k'aama pidolatuwaan, hawaa hinttenttoo s'aafaadditantto be'ite.  
\v 12 Asaa sintsan lo"iide beettanaw koyyiyaa ubbatuu, hintte k'as's'arettana mala koyyiino; shin hewaa unttunttu ootsiyaawe barenttoo Kiristtoosa mask'k'aliyaa diraw yederssettenaan attana s'alalaassa.  
\v 13 Ayaw gooppe, unttunttu hintte k'as's'aretteeddawaan c'eek'ettanaw hinttentta k'as's'arettino giinoppe attin, haray atto k'as's'aretteeddawanttukka barenttu huup'ew Muse higgiyaa naagikkino. 
\p  
\v 14 Shin alamii taw kak'ettina, taanikka alamew kak'etteedda Yesuusi Kiristtoosa mask'k'aliyaappe attin, taani c'eek'ettiyaabay harabay taappe haakko.  
\v 15 Ayaw gooppe, Kiristtoosi Yesuusan ooratsa med'etaa gidiyaawe maaddeeppe attin, k'as's'arettinakka k'as's'arettennaan agginakka ayinne maaddenna.  
\v 16 Ha wogaan hamettiyaa ubbatuwaa bollaninne S'oossaa asaa ubbaa bolla, sarotetsaynne maarotetsay gido. 
\p  
\v 17 Taani Yesuusaw maytteedda mallaa ta bollan tokkeedda diraw, hawaappe sintsaw itti asaykka taana metootsoppo. 
\p  
\v 18 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa aad'd'o keekatetsay hinttenttunna gido. Amen"i.